        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4290563985" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16936725742912779124">Yes this book can be finished in less than an hour. Quite in contrast to the amount of time an acorn takes to become a self respecting tree… <br/><br/>This book is a gem. Beyond its brevity it’s soul is the story - whether this is true ( or not ) does not matter. <br/><br/>After reading this you will want to believe such a person as Elzeard Bouffier actually lived and did what he did. <br/><br/>Cannot recommend it more for its pure simplicity of theme and its profoundly spiritual moral - ‘just do it ‘.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


