              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14828572391531760458">short but gold! the story definitely is here to teach us a lot of great things! whoever reads it will understand the greatness of a man&apos;s dedication and perseverance to achieve something great and bigger than one can imagine.<br/><br/>honestly one cannot possibly think he can achieve something without hard work and preservation. the mind and the soul should be strong and able to face the trouble they will encounter while working to achieve that goal! <br/><br/>doing good great things start with a small step one tak</span>
  <span id="freeText14828572391531760458" style="display:none">short but gold! the story definitely is here to teach us a lot of great things! whoever reads it will understand the greatness of a man's dedication and perseverance to achieve something great and bigger than one can imagine.<br /><br />honestly one cannot possibly think he can achieve something without hard work and preservation. the mind and the soul should be strong and able to face the trouble they will encounter while working to achieve that goal! <br /><br />doing good great things start with a small step one take so it shouldn't be underestimated:) <br /> <br /></span>
